                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9452" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1424</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1663 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">高瞻远瞩：海尔入主“血王”谋新篇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Long sighted and Far sighted: Haier’s Entry into the “Blood King” Strategy for a New Chapter</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">胡建雄，吴艺文，葛佳慧，张一恒，曹頔</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海尔集团公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海尔集团；海尔大健康；企业并购</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ier Group; Haier Health; Corporate mergers and acquisitions</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">目前，我国家电品类渗透率高，家电市场高度成熟。行业进入存量市场且竞争激烈的背景下，家电巨头纷纷跨界医疗领域，推动主业高质量发展的同时，积极开辟蓝海市场，打造第二增长点。作为国内家电龙头企业——海尔集团，于2005年便早已瞄准医疗领域，打造大健康生态品牌“盈康一生”，开启跨界转型之路。2024年6月海尔集团以总价125亿人民币成功收购基立福持有的上海莱士20%的股份，并获得26.58%的表决权，海尔已成为上海莱士的实际控制人，助推海尔打通血液制品发展壁垒，完善大健康产业版图。通过本案例教学，带领学员回顾海尔集团与上海莱士的并购案，着重聚焦于海尔在上海莱士存在若干风险情况下选择并购的动因，分析并购交易价格合理性，探讨并购过程中如何实现价值创造，旨在培养学员对于类似并购事件的综合分析能力，同时也为其他家电企业跨界从医、并购转型决策提供一定的参考价值。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">At present, the penetration rate of home appliance categories in China is high, and the home appliance market is highly mature. Against the backdrop of entering the existing market and fierce competition, home appliance giants are crossing the medical field one after another, promoting high-quality development of their main business while actively opening up blue ocean markets and creating a second growth point. As a leading domestic household appliance enterprise, Haier Group has been targeting the medical field since 2005, creating a big health ecological brand “Yingkang Yisheng” and embarking on a cross-border transformation path. In June 2024, Haier Group successfully acquired 20% of the shares of Shanghai Laishi held by Grifols at a total price of 12.5 billion yuan and obtained 26.58% of the voting rights, and Haier has become the actual controller of Shanghai Laishi, help Haier break through the development barriers of blood products, and improve the map of the big health industry. Through this case study, we will lead the students to review the merger and acquisition case between Haier Group and Shanghai Laishi, focusing on the reasons why Haier chose to merge with Shanghai Laishi in the face of various risks. We will analyze the rationality of the merger and acquisition transaction price, explore how to achieve value creation in the merger and acquisition process, and aim to cultivate students’ comprehensive analysis ability for similar merger and acquisition events. At the same time, it will also provide certain reference value for other home appliance enterprises to make cross-border medical and merger and acquisition transformation decisions.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业并购与重组》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">并购风险；并购动因；并购定价——市场法；并购整合</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
